                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890114-68-off352 t17890114-68-cd353"></join> last, ten hens, value 10 s. three cocks, value 5 s. two ducks and a drake, value 3 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17890114-68-victim674" type="victimName">
